*eix-0.32.1 (29 Oct 2016)

  29 Oct 2016; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> +eix-0.32.1.ebuild:
  version bump, fixes some bugs

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0

  06 Nov 2016; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> eix-0.32.1.ebuild:
  Major ebuild cleanup

  Clean up the ebuild: wrap and sort values, shorten description,
  improve readability, use bash syntax, add a lot of missing ||die,
  simplify awkward logic and kill double negations.

  06 Nov 2016; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> eix-0.32.1.ebuild:
  Remove invalid and useless USE flags

  Remove the USE flags violating different QA policies or being useless,
  in particular: flags used to control *FLAGS, flags used to alter
  configuration file, flags used to switch between building separate
  executables and symlinks to one executable.

  For the former, unconditionally disable altering user's *FLAGS. For
  the latter, force the defaults.

*eix-0.32.1-r1 (06 Nov 2016)

  06 Nov 2016; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> -eix-0.32.1.ebuild,
  +eix-0.32.1-r1.ebuild:
  Own the cache directory

